# .NET
[Bb]in/
# petbox-wire npm launcher lives in bin/ — not a .NET build dir; keep it tracked so the
# published package (and a clean CI checkout) carries it.
!src/clients-ts/petbox-wire/bin/
!src/clients-ts/petbox-wire/bin/**
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
